Serdisp version 0.01
=======================

This module got one main purpose. Communicate with a display
on the other side of the serdisplib.

This module is very alpha but patches are welcome.

See t/01-Serdisp.t for a very basic example!

This module was mainly build for the ct-maeusekino (inclu.de display).
But this library should run with other too.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Gd (C library AND(!) perl module)
  serdisplib (C library)

